The Assistant file contains the Obfuscator.xx trojan. That is NOT a goddamned FALSE POSITIVE.

I've been doing this since the 90's, I know as well as anyone that keygens and cracks tend to flag with false positives. It's just part of the game But 34/43 on VT, multiple reports of obfuscator (a rather nasty trojan), and VT community comments saying it infected their system seems like more than a false positive.
